<H1>Operating system</H1>

<P>An operating system is the program that controls all the
other parts of a computer system - both the hardware and
the software. Most importantly, it allows you to make use
of the facilities provided by the system.  Every computer
has an operating system.</P>

<P>The UNIX operating system has three important features; a
kernel, the shell and a filesystem.</P>

